# MDC: Agents Module
**Path:** `src/agents/`
**Purpose:** V3 agent stubs — interfaces only. All raise `NotImplementedError` in V1.

---

## IMPORTANT: V1 Behavior

All agents raise `NotImplementedError` in V1.
The module exists to define interfaces and enforce cognitive boundaries.
No agent logic runs until `PIPELINE_VERSION=v3`.

In V1, the pipeline uses `src/generate/v1_generator.py` and `src/evaluate/judge.py` directly.

