## Agent Cognitive Boundaries

These are the most important rules in this file. Each agent has exactly one cognitive task.

```
RESEARCHER  → competitive intelligence only. Never writes, edits, or evaluates copy.
WRITER      → first-draft creation only. Never edits existing copy.
EDITOR      → targeted improvement only. Never creates from a blank brief.
EVALUATOR   → quality judgment only. Never generates, edits, or suggests improvements.
ORCHESTRATOR → routing and coordination only. Makes no creative or evaluative decisions.
```

### Model Assignments (non-negotiable)

```
Researcher  → gemini-1.5-flash
Writer      → gemini-1.5-flash
Editor      → gemini-1.5-flash
Evaluator   → claude-sonnet-4-6    ← NEVER change this, even in V3
Orchestrator → no LLM calls — pure coordination logic
```

