## Agent Data Models

```python
class CreativeIntelligenceReport(BaseModel):
    brief_id:             str
    winning_hooks:        List[HookPattern]
    winning_ctas:         List[str]
    emotional_angles:     List[str]
    competitor_gaps:      List[str]
    recommended_approach: str
    confidence:           float
    created_at:           str

class HookPattern(BaseModel):
    style:      str
    example:    str
    competitor: str
    frequency:  int       # times observed across scraped ads

class OrchestratorResult(BaseModel):
    status:           str         # "published" / "abandoned" / "skipped"
    ad:               Ad
    evaluation:       EvaluationResult
    attempts:         int
    intelligence_used: bool
    total_cost_usd:   float
```

