## Test Specification

### `tests/unit/test_agents.py`

```
Version gating (all must raise NotImplementedError in V1)
- ResearcherAgent.research() → NotImplementedError
- WriterAgent.write()        → NotImplementedError
- EditorAgent.edit()         → NotImplementedError
- EvaluatorAgent.evaluate()  → NotImplementedError
- OrchestratorAgent.run_brief() → NotImplementedError

Interface compliance
- ResearcherAgent is subclass of BaseAgent
- WriterAgent is subclass of BaseAgent
- EditorAgent is subclass of BaseAgent
- EvaluatorAgent is subclass of BaseAgent
- OrchestratorAgent is subclass of BaseAgent

Model validation
- CreativeIntelligenceReport with all required fields → valid
- HookPattern with style, example, competitor, frequency → valid
- OrchestratorResult status accepts "published", "abandoned", "skipped"
- OrchestratorResult status rejects other strings → ValidationError
```

